errors.why_is_this_secret_unavailable: He aha tēnei karere huna kāore e wātea?
errors.secrets_are_designed_to_be_viewed_only_o: Kua hoahoatia ngā karere huna kia kitea kotahi noa te wā. Kua urunga pea tēnei hononga, kua pau, kua mukua ā-ringa rānei e te kaituku.
errors.contact_the_person_who_sent_you_this_lin: Whakapā atu ki te tangata nāna i tuku tēnei hononga, ā, tonoa ki te waihanga i tētahi karere huna hou. Kia mōhio rātou kāore koe i taea te uru ki ngā mōhiohio taketake.
errors.oops_the_page_you_are_looking_for_doesnt: Auē! Kāore te whārangi e rapu ana koe i te tīari, kua nekehia rānei.
errors.if_youre_unsure_what_to_do_next_please_f: Mēnā kāore koe e tino mōhio me aha koe ā muri ake nei, tēnā whai ake ki te tangata nāna i tuku tēnei hononga mō ētahi atu mōhiohio.
errors.information_shared_through_our_service_c: Ko ngā mōhiohio i tuari mā tā mātou ratonga ka taea te uru kotahi anake. Ka tirohia ana, ka mukua pūmautia te ihirangi mai i ā mātou tūmau hei whakaū i te noho muna. Ka āwhina tēnei huarahi ki te tiaki i ō raraunga tairongo mā te whakawhāiti i tōna whakaaturanga me te ārai i te urunga whakaaetia-kore.
errors.were_sorry_but_an_unexpected_error_occur: E whakapāha ana mātou, engari i puta he hapa ohorere i te wā o te tukatuka i tō tono. Kua whakamōhiotia tō mātou rōpū, ā, kei te mahi mātou ki te whakatika.
errors.go_share_a_secret: Haere tuari i tētahi karere huna!
errors.the_page_youre_looking_for_doesnt_exist_: Kāore te whārangi e rapu ana koe i te tīari, kua nekehia rānei. Kaua e māharahara, ka pā tēnei ki te pai rawa o tātou!
errors.unable_to_load_data_due_to_data_format_i: Kāore e taea te uta raraunga nā ngā take whakatakotoranga raraunga. Tēnā ngana anō ā muri ake.
